  <entry>
    <title>tranquilpea 书写篇</title>
    <link href="http://jiangyue.club/2017/05/19/tranquilpea-%E4%B9%A6%E5%86%99%E7%AF%87/"/>
    <id>http://jiangyue.club/2017/05/19/tranquilpea-书写篇/</id>
    <published>2017-05-19T08:49:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-15T08:04:45.829Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://louisbarranqueiro.github.io/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tranquilpeak</a>主题美观简洁，支持多种方式展示图片，适合图文并茂的博客。支持视频播放、字体元素、颜色、代码着色等功能<br><a id="more"></a></p><h5 id="1-alert-警告消息"><a href="#1-alert-警告消息" class="headerlink" title="1.alert 警告消息"></a>1.alert 警告消息</h5><ul><li><p>提示</p><div class="alert info no-icon"><p>增加一条不带图标的提示</p></div>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% alert info no-icon %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endalert %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>成功</p><div class="alert success no-icon"><p>增加一条不带图标的成功提示</p></div>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% alert success no-icon %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endalert %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>警告</p><div class="alert warning"><p>增加一条带图标的警告提示</p></div>    <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% alert warning %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endalert %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>严重警告 | 危险  </p><div class="alert danger"><p>增加一条带图片的危险警告</p></div>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% alert danger %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endalert %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><!-- more --><h5 id="2-HighlightText-高亮文本"><a href="#2-HighlightText-高亮文本" class="headerlink" title="2.HighlightText 高亮文本"></a>2.HighlightText 高亮文本</h5><ul><li>支持高亮颜色 color<ol><li>red</li><li>green</li><li>blue</li><li>purple</li><li>orange</li><li>yellow</li><li>cyan</li><li>primary</li><li>success</li><li>warning</li><li>danger</li></ol></li></ul><ul><li><p>语法：</p> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hl_text [(classes | hexa code | rgb color | rgba color)] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">content</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endhl_text %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>使用颜色 Class<span class="highlight-text danger">highlighted text danger</span><span class="highlight-text red">highlighted text red</span></li><li>使用自定义颜色<span class="highlight-text" style="background-color:#00FFFF;">highlighted text  #00FFFF</span><span class="highlight-text" style="background-color:#37fc21;">highlighted text  #00FFFF</span></li></ol></li></ul><h5 id="3-增加图像画廊"><a href="#3-增加图像画廊" class="headerlink" title="3.增加图像画廊"></a>3.增加图像画廊</h5><ul><li><p>语法：</p><pre><code>{% image fancybox center fig-100 group:travel image2.png http://s15.sinaimg.cn/mw690/001MXOZUgy6DUbyFxgy7e&690 "图像标题" %}</code></pre></li></ul><h5 id="4-标签代码块"><a href="#4-标签代码块" class="headerlink" title="4.标签代码块"></a>4.标签代码块</h5><ul><li><p>语法：</p> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123; ％ tabbed_codeblock [name] [link] ％ &#125;</span><br><span class="line">     &lt;！ - tab [lang] - &gt;</span><br><span class="line">        源代码</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;！ - endtab - &gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;％ endtabbed_codeblock％ &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="codeblock codeblock--tabbed"><figcaption><a href="http://jiangyue.club">example</a><ul class="tabs"><li class="tab active">js</li><li class="tab">css</li></ul></figcaption><div class="tabs-content"><figure class="highlight js" style="display: block;"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> test = <span class="string">'test'</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class="highlight css" style="display: none;"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.btn</span> {</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attribute">color</span>: red;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></div></figure></li></ul><h5 id="5-文章显示方式"><a href="#5-文章显示方式" class="headerlink" title="5.文章显示方式"></a>5.文章显示方式</h5><ul><li><p>语法：</p><ul><li><p>截断文章的全文展示</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>使文章已内容表展示 可添加在标题后面</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!-- toc --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://louisbarranqueiro.github.io/hexo-theme-tranquilpeak/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;Tranquilpeak&lt;/a&gt;主题美观简洁，支持多种方式展示图片，适合图文并茂的博客。支持视频播放、字体元素、颜色、代码着色等功能&lt;br&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
      <category term="tranquilpeak" scheme="http://jiangyue.club/categories/tranquilpeak/"/>
    
    
      <category term="tranquilpeak" scheme="http://jiangyue.club/tags/tranquilpeak/"/>
    
